<p data-start="179" data-end="197">Key visual change:</p>
<ul data-start="198" data-end="376">
<li data-section-id="nx4vom" data-start="198" data-end="249">
<p data-start="200" data-end="249">envelope now looks like a <strong data-start="226" data-end="249">folded paper letter</strong></p>
