<h2 data-section-id="1kxw8xp" data-start="490" data-end="527">🔇 Why you still might not hear it</h2>
<p data-start="529" data-end="603">Even though everything is correct, your current setup has 2 common issues:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="5kiyp8" data-start="605" data-end="640">1. That audio file is very soft</h3>
<p data-start="641" data-end="740"><code data-start="641" data-end="670">mixkit-paper-slide-1531.mp3</code> is a <strong data-start="676" data-end="697">very subtle sound</strong>, so on phone/laptop it often feels silent.</p>
<hr data-start="742" data-end="745">
<h3 data-section-id="1c9xf86" data-start="747" data-end="775">2. No volume control set</h3>
<p data-start="776" data-end="836">Some browsers reduce perceived volume unless explicitly set.</p>
