<p data-start="104" data-end="191">At this point, there are only a few real causes left, and I’ll fix it properly for you.</p>
<hr data-start="193" data-end="196">
<h1 data-section-id="1ri32ao" data-start="198" data-end="228">🔴 WHY IT STILL DOESN’T PLAY</h1>
<p data-start="230" data-end="279">Even with correct code, Chrome/Edge often blocks:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1wyas8q" data-start="281" data-end="333">1. ❌ Remote audio files (CORS / autoplay policy)</h3>
<p data-start="334" data-end="432">Some CDNs (including Mixkit / Pixabay / SoundJay) silently block direct playback inside <code data-start="422" data-end="431">&lt;audio&gt;</code>.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="qd9i71" data-start="434" data-end="477">2. ❌ play() triggered after DOM changes</h3>
<p data-start="478" data-end="555">You open overlay + then play sound → some browsers “break” the gesture chain.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="11jtwb5" data-start="557" data-end="590">3. ❌ No “user gesture unlock”</h3>
<p data-start="591" data-end="656">Mobile browsers often require a <strong data-start="623" data-end="656">first interaction unlock step</strong></p>
<hr data-start="658" data-end="661">
<h1 data-section-id="1llokze" data-start="663" data-end="703">✅ THE 100% WORKING FIX (REAL SOLUTION)</h1>
<p data-start="705" data-end="778">We’ll do what real apps do:<br data-start="732" data-end="735">
👉 <strong data-start="738" data-end="778">unlock audio on first click globally</strong></p>
<hr data-start="780" data-end="783">
