<h2 data-section-id="r31gtl" data-start="1594" data-end="1646"><span role="text">🎧 STEP 4 — Update your <code data-start="1621" data-end="1635">openLetter()</code> sound code</span></h2>
<p data-start="1648" data-end="1677">Replace your sound part with:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1679" data-end="2023"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">document</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>getElementById(</span><span class="ͼz">"paperSound"</span><span>);</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">try</span><span> {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>pause();</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>currentTime </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>volume </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">1.0</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">playPromise</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>play();</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">if</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼ11">playPromise</span><span>) {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼ11">playPromise</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>catch(</span><span class="ͼ11">err</span><span> =&gt; {</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼ11">console</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>log(</span><span class="ͼz">"Brave blocked audio:"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">err</span><span>);</span><br><span>        });</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>} </span><span class="ͼv">catch</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼ11">e</span><span>) {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">console</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>log(</span><span class="ͼ11">e</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2025" data-end="2028">
<h1 data-section-id="lnmv5a" data-start="2030" data-end="2058">🟢 WHY THIS WORKS IN BRAVE</h1>
<p data-start="2060" data-end="2186">✔ local file (no CDN blocking)<br data-start="2090" data-end="2093">
✔ first-click unlock bypass<br data-start="2120" data-end="2123">
✔ avoids autoplay restrictions<br data-start="2153" data-end="2156">
✔ works even with Shields ON</p>
<hr data-start="2188" data-end="2191">
<h1 data-section-id="1pf7ynt" data-start="2193" data-end="2209">💡 QUICK CHECK</h1>
<p data-start="2211" data-end="2236">If it STILL doesn’t play:</p>
<ul data-start="2238" data-end="2355">
<li data-section-id="14r3yao" data-start="2238" data-end="2294">
<p data-start="2240" data-end="2294">Click 🔒 icon in Brave → <strong data-start="2265" data-end="2294">Shields OFF for this site</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1l3m40d" data-start="2295" data-end="2315">
<p data-start="2297" data-end="2315">Check volume mixer</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="eoonk8" data-start="2316" data-end="2355">
<p data-start="2318" data-end="2355">Try right-click tab → <strong data-start="2340" data-end="2355">Unmute site</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2357" data-end="2360">
<h1 data-section-id="1i4bizw" data-start="2362" data-end="2378">❤️ Bottom line</h1>
<p data-start="2380" data-end="2405">This is not your mistake.</p>
<p data-start="2407" data-end="2471">👉 Brave is just aggressively privacy-protecting media playback.</p>
<hr data-start="2473" data-end="2476">
