<hr data-start="1492" data-end="1495">
<h1 data-section-id="1rir373" data-start="1497" data-end="1528">💡 WHY THIS WORKS (IMPORTANT)</h1>
<p data-start="1530" data-end="1560">This fixes everything because:</p>
<ul data-start="1562" data-end="1742">
<li data-section-id="1n9vujx" data-start="1562" data-end="1613">
<p data-start="1564" data-end="1613">✔ No external audio files (Brave cannot block it)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19r4yd8" data-start="1614" data-end="1643">
<p data-start="1616" data-end="1643">✔ No autoplay policy issues</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="85peop" data-start="1644" data-end="1681">
<p data-start="1646" data-end="1681">✔ Runs inside browser engine itself</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sr9181" data-start="1682" data-end="1742">
<p data-start="1684" data-end="1742">✔ Works on ALL devices (mobile + desktop + Brave + Safari)</p>
</li>
</ul>
