<p data-start="95" data-end="252">Right now you’re hearing a <strong data-start="122" data-end="153">synthetic beep (oscillator)</strong>, not a real paper sound because Web Audio API by itself can’t magically create realistic textures.</p>
<p data-start="254" data-end="281">So we’ll fix this properly.</p>
<hr data-start="283" data-end="286">
<h1 data-section-id="uvvkgb" data-start="288" data-end="344">🎯 BEST SOLUTION (REAL PAPER SOUND, STILL BRAVE-PROOF)</h1>
<p data-start="346" data-end="357">We combine:</p>
<ul data-start="358" data-end="466">
<li data-section-id="1x1chmc" data-start="358" data-end="401">
<p data-start="360" data-end="401">✔ Web Audio API (for Brave compatibility)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f2o7gp" data-start="402" data-end="466">
<p data-start="404" data-end="466">✔ REAL recorded paper sound (so it actually sounds like paper)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="468" data-end="471">
