pan></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="request-6a2bade7-35c8-83e8-82cc-ecc224aeb089-16" data-is-intersecting="true" style="--last-known-height: 72px;"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-6a2bade7-35c8-83e8-82cc-ecc224aeb089-16" data-turn-id-container="request-6a2bade7-35c8-83e8-82cc-ecc224aeb089-16" data-testid="conversation-turn-38" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="8f2b947c-da03-4da9-893a-36755f2d1ccf" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3-mini" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="101">Short answer: <strong data-start="14" data-end="101">no — you can’t (and shouldn’t) “edit Brave” to force autoplay sound from a webpage.</strong></p>
<p data-start="103" data-end="190">But I’ll explain clearly what <em data-start="133" data-end="137">is</em> possible and what the correct long-term solution is.</p>
<hr data-start="192" data-end="195">
<h1 data-section-id="d1ueps" data-start="197" data-end="227">🚫 Why you can’t “fix Brave”</h1>
<p data-start="229" data-end="269">Brave is designed to block exactly this:</p>
<ul data-start="271" data-end="383">
<li data-section-id="1biphx1" data-start="271" data-end="287">
<p data-start="273" data-end="287">autoplay audio</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="z8o2bg" data-start="288" data-end="314">
<p data-start="290" data-end="314">hidden background sounds</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11bxvcu" data-start="315" data-end="339">
<p data-start="317" data-end="339">external media streams</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hk791q" data-start="340" data-end="383">
<p data-start="342" data-end="383">scripts trying to auto-play without trust</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="385" data-end="480">Even if you “change settings,” Brave will still enforce:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="445" data-end="480">user-gesture based audio policy</strong></p>
<p data-start="482" data-end="497">So there is no:</p>
<ul data-start="498" data-end="582">
<li data-section-id="16cezvy" data-start="498" data-end="512">
<p data-start="500" data-end="512">config tweak</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j3470p" data-start="513" data-end="519">
<p data-start="515" data-end="519">hack</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fjuq91" data-start="520" data-end="582">
<p data-start="522" data-end="582">setting<br>
that permanently allows auto-sound for all websites.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="584" data-end="619">That would defeat browser security.</p>
<hr data-start="621" data-end="624">
<h1 data-section-id="1bjrw8a" data-start="626" data-end="672">✅ What you SHOULD do instead (real solution)</h1>
<p data-start="674" data-end="744">For projects like yours (lots of sounds), the correct architecture is:</p>
<h2 data-section-id="dtn82n" data-start="746" data-end="788">🧠 1. Unlock audio once (global unlock)</h2>
<p data-start="789" data-end="839">You already started this — this is the right idea.</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="841" data-end="915"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼ11">document</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>addEventListener(</span><span class="ͼz">"click"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">unlockAudio</span><span>, { once: </span><span class="ͼy">true</span><span> });</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="917" data-end="997">This gives your site “permission” to play audio forever after first interaction.</p>
<hr data-start="999" data-end="1002">
<h2 data-section-id="19b2kq8" data-start="1004" data-end="1064">🎧 2. Use ONE shared audio manager (important for future)</h2>
<p data-start="1066" data-end="1117">Instead of many broken sounds, you create a system:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1ra7yz3" data-start="1119" data-end="1155">Example (future-proof approach):</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1157" data-end="1666"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">let</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">soundUnlocked</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">false</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼv">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">sounds</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> {};</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">initSounds</span><span>() {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sounds</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>paper </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">new</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">Audio</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼz">"paper.mp3"</span><span>);</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sounds</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>paper</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>volume </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">1.0</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sounds</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>pop </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">new</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">Audio</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼz">"pop.mp3"</span><span>);</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sounds</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>pop</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>volume </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">1.0</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">unlockAudio</span><span>() {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">if</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼ11">soundUnlocked</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼv">return</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">initSounds</span><span>();</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">// prime audio</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">Object</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>values(</span><span class="ͼ11">sounds</span><span>)</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>forEach(</span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span> =&gt; {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>play()</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>then(() =&gt; {</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>pause();</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>currentTime </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>        })</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>catch(()=&gt;{});</span><br><span>    });</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">soundUnlocked</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">true</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1668" data-end="1671">
<h2 data-section-id="orj9la" data-start="1673" data-end="1710">🔊 3. Always play sound like this:</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1712" data-end="1845"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">play</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ11">name</span><span>) {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">sounds</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼ11">name</span><span>];</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">if</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼv">!</span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼv">return</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>currentTime </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">s</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>play()</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>catch(()=&gt;{});</span><br><span>}</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1847" data-end="1850">
<h1 data-section-id="1fw2lga" data-start="1852" data-end="1886">💡 Why this is the REAL solution</h1>
<p data-start="1888" data-end="1909">Because it gives you:</p>
<p data-start="1911" data-end="2060">✔ works in Brave<br data-start="1927" data-end="1930">
✔ works in Chrome<br data-start="1947" data-end="1950">
✔ works in mobile<br data-start="1967" data-end="1970">
✔ scalable for many sounds<br data-start="1996" data-end="1999">
✔ no browser hacks needed<br data-start="2024" data-end="2027">
✔ no breaking in future updates</p>
<hr data-start="2062" data-end="2065">
<h1 data-section-id="155tsn9" data-start="2067" data-end="2085">❌ What NOT to do</h1>
<ul data-start="2087" data-end="2228">
<li data-section-id="1h550qq" data-start="2087" data-end="2127">
<p data-start="2089" data-end="2127">don’t try to disable Brave protections</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="igtbu7" data-start="2128" data-end="2159">
<p data-start="2130" data-end="2159">don’t rely on CDN audio links</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cy8za2" data-start="2160" data-end="2186">
<p data-start="2162" data-end="2186">don’t use autoplay hacks</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qqpay0" data-start="2187" data-end="2228">
<p data-start="2189" data-end="2228">don’t use random external sound sources</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2230" data-end="2233">
<h1 data-section-id="3ovecs" data-start="2235" data-end="2252">❤️ Simple truth</h1>
<p data-start="2254" data-end="2354">Browsers will <em data-start="2268" data-end="2315">never allow forced audio autoplay permanently</em> — not Brave, Chrome, Safari, anything.</p>
<p data-start="2356" data-end="2460">So the correct approach is:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="2387" data-end="2460">build an audio system that works WITH browser rules, not against them</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2462" data-end="2465">
<h1 data-section-id="kwvj22" data-start="2467" data-end="2502">🚀 If you want next level upgrade</h1>
<p data-start="2504" data-end="2548">I can <span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">convert your whole project into</span></span>:</p>
<p data-start="2550" data-end="2574">✨ “mini love app engine”</p>
<ul data-start="2575" data-end="2736">
<li data-section-id="1czan8k" data-start="2575" data-end="2599">
<p data-start="2577" data-end="2599">multiple sound library</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14muh9y" data-start="2600" data-end="2620">
