<h2 data-section-id="4vzz54" data-start="476" data-end="511">🔊 Then your audio link becomes:</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="513" data-end="576"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>https://your-username.github.io/your-repo/paper.mp3</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="578" data-end="581">
<h1 data-section-id="2nl67k" data-start="583" data-end="595">🧠 EXAMPLE</h1>
<p data-start="597" data-end="600">If:</p>
<ul data-start="601" data-end="647">
<li data-section-id="17hz0gg" data-start="601" data-end="623">
<p data-start="603" data-end="623">username = <code data-start="614" data-end="623">john123</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sius19" data-start="624" data-end="647">
<p data-start="626" data-end="647">repo = <code data-start="633" data-end="647">love-letters</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="649" data-end="654">Then:</p>
