>
<hr data-start="129" data-end="132">
<h1 data-section-id="1q85rpx" data-start="134" data-end="145">✅ 🎯 GOAL</h1>
<p data-start="146" data-end="220">Make your envelope click play a <strong data-start="178" data-end="220">real paper sound from your GitHub site</strong></p>
<hr data-start="222" data-end="225">
<h1 data-section-id="5f7s9t" data-start="227" data-end="265">🟢 STEP 1 — Add audio file to GitHub</h1>
<p data-start="267" data-end="320">Go to your GitHub repository (where <code data-start="303" data-end="315">index.html</code> is).</p>
<h3 data-section-id="nyb8p3" data-start="322" data-end="334">➕ Click:</h3>
<ul data-start="335" data-end="364">
<li data-section-id="wmau5n" data-start="335" data-end="364">
<p data-start="337" data-end="364"><strong data-start="337" data-end="364">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1hjtf6v" data-start="366" data-end="380">📥 Upload:</h3>
<p data-start="381" data-end="407">Rename your sound file to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="409" data-end="430"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>paper.mp3</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="432" data-end="447">Then upload it.</p>
<hr data-start="449" data-end="452">
<h1 data-section-id="1svipxy" data-start="454" data-end="488">🟢 STEP 2 — Check repo structure</h1>
<p data-start="490" data-end="522">Your repo should look like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="524" data-end="571"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>index.html</span><br><span>paper.mp3</span><br><span>other files...</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="573" data-end="640">⚠️ Important: <code data-start="587" data-end="598">paper.mp3</code> must be in the SAME level as <code data-start="628" data-end="640">index.html</code></p>
<hr data-start="642" data-end="645">
<h1 data-section-id="km0k0l" data-start="647" data-end="681">🟢 STEP 3 — Turn on GitHub Pages</h1>
<p data-start="683" data-end="706">If not already enabled:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="cck52n" data-start="708" data-end="718">Go to:</h3>
<ul data-start="719" data-end="815">
<li data-section-id="5irq1j" data-start="719" data-end="736">
<p data-start="721" data-end="736">Repo → Settings</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lnmlk6" data-start="737" data-end="754">
<p data-start="739" data-end="754">Click <strong data-start="745" data-end="754">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="oowav9" data-start="755" data-end="802">
<p data-start="757" data-end="779">Under “Branch” select:</p>
<ul data-start="782" data-end="802">
<li data-section-id="18ag83n" data-start="782" data-end="790">
<p data-start="784" data-end="790"><code data-start="784" data-end="790">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cwgn7l" data-start="793" data-end="802">
<p data-start="795" data-end="802"><code data-start="795" data-end="802">/root</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16f4fxj" data-start="803" data-end="815">
<p data-start="805" data-end="815">Click Save</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="817" data-end="820">
<h1 data-section-id="17paepj" data-start="822" data-end="857">🟢 STEP 4 — Get your website link</h1>
<p data-start="859" data-end="895">GitHub will give you something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="897" data-end="951"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>https://your-username.github.io/your-repo/</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="953" data-end="956">
