<p data-start="991" data-end="1021">Replace/add this in your code:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1023" data-end="1129"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#fa6359" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><div role="group" aria-label="Code block view" class="group/code-block-preview-toggle relative flex items-center gap-0.5"><div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute start-0 top-0 size-9 rounded-full bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/10 motion-safe:transition-transform motion-safe:duration-200 motion-safe:ease-in-out translate-x-0 group-has-[[data-code-block-preview-toggle-preview]:hover]/code-block-preview-toggle:translate-x-[calc(100%+2px)] group-has-[[data-code-block-preview-toggle-preview]:focus-visible]/code-block-preview-toggle:translate-x-[calc(100%+2px)]"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative z-1 flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full motion-safe:transition-colors text-token-text-primary" data-code-block-preview-toggle-code="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative z-1 flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full motion-safe:transition-colors text-token-text-primary" data-code-block-preview-toggle-preview="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div data-custom-highlighting-behavior="boundary" class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative [container-type:inline-size]"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="max-height: 56.25cqw; transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼ13">&lt;audio</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">id</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"paperSound"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">preload</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"auto"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ13">&lt;source</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"paper.mp3"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">type</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"audio/mpeg"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼ13">&lt;/audio&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1131" data-end="1189">👉 This works because GitHub serves it from the same site.</p>
<hr data-start="1191" data-end="1194">
<h1 data-section-id="1wya4k5" data-start="1196" data-end="1230">🟢 STEP 6 — Add this JS function</h1>
<p data-start="1232" data-end="1255">Inside your <code data-start="1244" data-end="1254">&lt;script&gt;</code>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1257" data-end="1509"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">playPaperSound</span><span>() {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">document</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>getElementById(</span><span class="ͼz">"paperSound"</span><span>);</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>pause();</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>currentTime </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>volume </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">1.0</span><span>;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ11">sound</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>play()</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>catch(</span><span class="ͼ11">err</span><span> =&gt; {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼ11">console</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>log(</span><span class="ͼz">"Audio blocked:"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">err</span><span>);</span><br><span>    });</span><br><span>}</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1511" data-end="1514">
<h1 data-section-id="1xwbyfs" data-start="1516" data-end="1546">🟢 STEP 7 — Call it on click</h1>
<p data-start="1548" data-end="1584">Inside your envelope click function:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1586" data-end="1613"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼ11">playPaperSound</span><span>();</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1615" data-end="1618">
<h1 data-section-id="6ee7l3" data-start="1620" data-end="1648">🟢 STEP 8 — PUSH to GitHub</h1>
<ul data-start="1650" data-end="1718">
<li data-section-id="1dmcmh8" data-start="1650" data-end="1666">
<p data-start="1652" data-end="1666">Commit changes</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="o70hgu" data-start="1667" data-end="1685">
<p data-start="1669" data-end="1685">Wait 1–2 minutes</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="o34541" data-start="1686" data-end="1718">
<p data-start="1688" data-end="1718">Refresh your GitHub Pages link</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1720" data-end="1723">
<h1 data-section-id="1qmorst" data-start="1725" data-end="1753">🎧 DONE — IT WILL WORK NOW</h1>
<p data-start="1755" data-end="1770">When you click:</p>
<ul data-start="1771" data-end="1872">
<li data-section-id="1t7ob4" data-start="1771" data-end="1790">
<p data-start="1773" data-end="1790">envelope opens 💌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xy5v7h" data-start="1791" data-end="1813">
<p data-start="1793" data-end="1813">paper sound plays 🔊</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rl5xo5" data-start="1814" data-end="1872">
<p data-start="1816" data-end="1872">Brave will NOT block it (because it's local GitHub file)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1874" data-end="1877">
<h1 data-section-id="1qm95u2" data-start="1879" data-end="1908">⚠️ If it STILL doesn’t work</h1>
<p data-start="1910" data-end="1922">Check these:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1q1woh2" data-start="1924" data-end="1952">🔇 1. File name mismatch</h3>
<p data-start="1953" data-end="1969">Must be exactly:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1970" data-end="1991"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>paper.mp3</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="13exu8e" data-start="1993" data-end="2013">🔇 2. Wrong path</h3>
<p data-start="2014" data-end="2026">Must NOT be:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2027" data-end="2087"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>./assets/paper.mp3 ❌ (unless you created folder)</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="13uo4ir" data-start="2089" data-end="2111">🔇 3. Hard refresh</h3>
<p data-start="2112" data-end="2118">Press:</p>
