<p data-start="82" data-end="111">Follow this exactly in order.</p>
<hr data-start="113" data-end="116">
<h1 data-section-id="ng82sw" data-start="118" data-end="127">🎯 GOAL</h1>
<p data-start="128" data-end="206">Your envelope click should play a <strong data-start="162" data-end="182">real paper sound</strong> on your GitHub website.</p>
<hr data-start="208" data-end="211">
<h1 data-section-id="19ukrwe" data-start="213" data-end="248">🟢 STEP 1 — Download a sound file</h1>
<p data-start="250" data-end="282">We first need a real audio file.</p>
<p data-start="284" data-end="374">👉 Click this link:<br>
<a data-start="304" data-end="374" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://cdn.pixabay.com/download/audio/2022/03/15/audio_6c4b0a1c0e.mp3<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="376" data-end="390">When it opens:</p>
<ul data-start="391" data-end="429">
<li data-section-id="1je3kdj" data-start="391" data-end="418">
<p data-start="393" data-end="418">Right click → <strong data-start="407" data-end="418">Save As</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kwjnjc" data-start="419" data-end="429">
<p data-start="421" data-end="429">Name it:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="431" data-end="464"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>paper.mp3</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="466" data-end="469">
<h1 data-section-id="s2scfk" data-start="471" data-end="501">🟢 STEP 2 — Upload to GitHub</h1>
<p data-start="503" data-end="532">Go to your GitHub repository.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="79xya3" data-start="534" data-end="543">Then:</h3>
<ul data-start="544" data-end="600">
<li data-section-id="169w811" data-start="544" data-end="579">
<p data-start="546" data-end="579">Click <strong data-start="552" data-end="579">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="x39j4t" data-start="580" data-end="600">
<p data-start="582" data-end="600">Upload <code data-start="589" data-end="600">paper.mp3</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="602" data-end="605">
<h1 data-section-id="1j8hp4n" data-start="607" data-end="641">🟢 STEP 3 — Check repo structure</h1>
<p data-start="643" data-end="673">Your repo MUST look like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="675" data-end="719"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>index.html</span><br><span>paper.mp3</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="721" data-end="766">⚠️ Important: SAME level (not inside folders)</p>
<hr data-start="768" data-end="771">
<h1 data-section-id="owwyc" data-start="773" data-end="808">🟢 STEP 4 — Add audio tag in HTML</h1>
<p data-start="810" data-end="845">Inside your <code data-start="822" data-end="834">index.html</code>, add this:</p>
